靠伏首称臣来控制它？
I control it by surrendering control? That doesn't make any sense.

577
00:41:16,470 --> 00:41:17,890
根本没道理

578
00:41:18,140 --> 00:41:20,440
万物并非皆有道理 也非必有道理
Not everything does. Not everything has to.

579
00:41:21,180 --> 00:41:23,690
你的才智让你成就傲人
Your intellect has taken you far in life...

580
00:41:23,850 --> 00:41:25,320
但仅止于此
But it will take you no further.

581
00:41:25,810 --> 00:41:27,810
伏首称臣吧 史蒂芬
Surrender, Stephen.

582
00:41:28,270 --> 00:41:30,020
放下你的自我
Silence your ego...

583
00:41:30,320 --> 00:41:32,190
力量就会油然而生
And your power will rise.

584
00:41:32,900 --> 00:41:34,250
跟我来
Come with me.

585
00:41:39,370 --> 00:41:40,460
等一下
Wait.

586
00:41:40,540 --> 00:41:42,500
- 这是… - 圣母峰
-Is this... -Everest.

587
00:41:44,040 --> 00:41:45,180
好美
Beautiful.

588
00:41:45,210 --> 00:41:47,760
对 美呆了
Yeah, right, beautiful.

589
00:41:47,920 --> 00:41:50,340
冷毙了 但很美
Freezing but beautiful.

590
00:41:50,500 --> 00:41:51,860
在这种温度下
At this temperature...

591
00:41:51,880 --> 00:41:54,010
一个人只能撑30分钟
A person can last for 30 minutes...

592
00:41:54,090 --> 00:41:56,680
然后永久失去身体机能
Before suffering permanent loss of function.

593
00:41:56,930 --> 00:41:57,930
好极了
Great.

594
00:41:58,010 --> 00:42:00,480
不过两分钟就可能休克
But you'll likely go into shock within the first two.

595
00:42:01,760 --> 00:42:03,890
什么？ 伏首称臣吧 史蒂芬
What?

596
00:42:04,060 --> 00:42:05,110
不！
Surrender, Stephen.

597
00:42:04,274 --> 00:42:05,364
No!

598
00:42:14,940 --> 00:42:16,100
菜鸟的表现如何？
How's our new recruit?

599
00:42:16,700 --> 00:42:18,240
等着瞧
We shall see.

600
00:42:19,030 --> 00:42:20,750
马上就会看到
Any second now.

601
00:42:22,910 --> 00:42:24,130
最好别再来一遍
No, not again.

602
00:42:29,460 --> 00:42:30,460
或许我该…
Maybe I should...

603
00:43:44,660 --> 00:43:45,710
史蒂芬
Stephen.

604
00:43:45,950 --> 00:43:46,950
王
Wong.

605
00:43:47,040 --> 00:43:48,060
你要什么 史传奇？
What do you want, strange?

606
00:43:48,080 --> 00:43:49,500
灵魂出窍的书
Books on astral projection.

607
00:43:50,540 --> 00:43:51,590
你还没准备好
You're not ready for that.

608
00:43:52,210 --> 00:43:54,010
放马过来 碧昂丝
Try me, Beyoncé.

609
00:43:56,800 --> 00:43:58,470
少来 你一定听过她
Oh, come on. You've heard of her.

610
00:43:58,550 --> 00:43:59,930
她是流行天后耶
She's a huge star, right?

611
00:44:02,680 --> 00:44:03,890
你这辈子笑过吗？
Do you ever laugh?

612
00:44:05,140 --> 00:44:06,770
快点 拿书给我
Come on, just give me the book.

613
00:44:07,810 --> 00:44:08,900
不行
No.

614
00:44:36,250 --> 00:44:38,000
你曾经在这里
Once, in this room, you begged me to let you learn.

615
00:44:38,090 --> 00:44:40,430
求我让你学习

616
00:44:40,880 --> 00:44:43,430
现在我却听说你质疑每项课程
Now, I'm told you question every lesson...

617
00:44:43,510 --> 00:44:45,100
宁可自学
Preferring to teach yourself.

618
00:44:45,390 --> 00:44:47,160
你曾经在这里叫我睁开眼睛
Once, in this room, you told me to open my eye.

619
00:44:47,180 --> 00:44:49,100
现在却又叫我盲目接受…
Now, I'm being told to blindly accept rules...

620
00:44:49,310 --> 00:44:50,600
毫无道理的规定
That make no sense.

621
00:44:50,930 --> 00:44:53,730
像是不准在图书馆里召唤入口？
Like the rule against conjuring a gateway in the library?

622
00:44:53,980 --> 00:44:55,360
王打我小报告？
Wong told on me?

623
00:44:55,610 --> 00:44:58,030
你的法术能力进步神速
You're advancing quickly with your sorcery skills.

624
00:44:58,110 --> 00:45:00,780
需要安全的地方练习施咒
You need a safe space to practice your spells.

625
00:45:19,250 --> 00:45:21,260
你正在镜次元里
You are now inside the mirror dimension...

626
00:45:21,590 --> 00:45:24,090
它始终存在却无法察觉
Ever present but undetected.

627
00:45:24,300 --> 00:45:26,300
现实世界不受这里所影响
The real world isn't affected by what happens here.

628
00:45:28,260 --> 00:45:31,440
我们运用镜次元训练、监督
We use the mirror dimension to train, surveil...

629
00:45:32,230 --> 00:45:34,570
有时将威胁困住
And sometimes to contain threats.

630
00:45:34,640 --> 00:45:36,880
没有灵环被困在这里就惨了
You don't wanna be stuck in here without your sling ring.

631
00:45:36,980 --> 00:45:39,700
慢着 抱歉 你刚说威胁？
Hold on. Sorry. What do you mean, "threats?"

632
00:45:49,620 --> 00:45:53,460
学习无限的多重宇宙 也包括学习无限的危险
Learning of an infinite multiverse includes learning of infinite dangers.

633
00:45:54,290 --> 00:45:56,760
要是我把你不知道的事都告诉你
If I told you everything else that you don't already know...

634
00:45:56,830 --> 00:45:58,380
你会吓到逃走
You'd run from here in terror.

635
00:46:04,420 --> 00:46:06,850
她到底有多老？
So just how ancient is she?

636
00:46:09,180 --> 00:46:11,560
没有人知道至尊魔法师的年龄
No one knows the age of the sorcerer supreme.

637
00:46:12,520 --> 00:46:15,520
只知道她是凯尔特人 从不谈她的过去
Only that she's Celtic and never talks about her past.

638
00:46:15,690 --> 00:46:17,530
你追随她 连你都不知道？
You follow her, even though you don't know?

639
00:46:17,600 --> 00:46:18,650
我知道她稳如泰山
I know she's steadfast...

640
00:46:18,850 --> 00:46:20,280
却也难以预料
But unpredictable.

641
00:46:20,440 --> 00:46:21,740
无情却又仁慈
Merciless, yet kind.

642
00:46:23,900 --> 00:46:25,370
她造就了今天的我
She made me what I am.

643
00:46:27,030 --> 00:46:28,370
相信你的导师
Trust your teacher...

644
00:46:29,200 --> 00:46:30,250
不要迷失方向
And don't lose your way.

645
00:46:30,530 --> 00:46:31,530
像卡西流斯那样？
Like kaecilius?

646
00:46:31,950 --> 00:46:32,950
没错
That's right.

647
00:46:38,170 --> 00:46:39,210
你认识他
You knew him.

648
00:46:40,170 --> 00:46:41,250
他来找我们时
When he first came to us...

649
00:46:41,960 --> 00:46:43,550
他失去了所有心爱的人
He'd lost everyone he ever loved.

650
00:46:43,880 --> 00:46:47,550
他悲痛欲绝 想在秘术中寻找答案
He was a grieving, broken man

651
00:46:45,889 --> 00:46:47,719
searching for answers in the mystic arts.

652
00:46:47,630 --> 00:46:51,560
他是优秀的学生 却骄傲固执
A brilliant student, but he was proud, headstrong.

653
00:46:51,640 --> 00:46:53,720
质疑古一 拒绝她的指导
He questioned the ancient one, rejected her teaching.

654
00:47:01,310 --> 00:47:03,160
他离开了卡玛泰姬
He left kamar-taj.

655
00:47:03,230 --> 00:47:05,780
门徒像绵羊般跟随他
His disciples followed him like sheep. Seduced by false doctrine.

656
00:47:05,860 --> 00:47:07,830
受到错误教义的引诱

657
00:47:07,900 --> 00:47:10,330
他偷走禁忌仪式 对吧？
And he stole the forbidden ritual, right?

658
00:47:10,410 --> 00:47:11,410
对
Yes.

659
00:47:11,570 --> 00:47:12,750
那仪式是做什么的？
What did it do?

660
00:47:15,080 --> 00:47:16,420
不能再问了
No more questions.

661
00:47:17,910 --> 00:47:19,010
那是什么？
What's that?

662
00:47:19,080 --> 00:47:20,330
你又在问了
That's a question.

663
00:47:22,080 --> 00:47:23,930
这是一个法器
This is a relic.

664
00:47:24,090 --> 00:47:25,930
有的魔法太过强大
Some magic is too powerful to sustain...

665
00:47:26,090 --> 00:47:27,290
所以我们将它灌输到物体中
So we imbue objects with it...

666
00:47:28,340 --> 00:47:30,560
让法器代我们去承受
Allowing them to take the strain we cannot.

667
00:47:30,760 --> 00:47:33,600
这是…
This is the staff...

668
00:47:33,800 --> 00:47:35,400
生命法庭的权杖
Of the living tribunal.

669
00:47:39,190 --> 00:47:40,310
有许多法器
There are many relics.

670
00:47:41,100 --> 00:47:42,280
瓦图姆魔杖
The wand of watoomb.

671
00:47:42,610 --> 00:47:44,900
伏特尔的拱靴
The vaulting boots of valtorr.

672
00:47:45,150 --> 00:47:46,900
念起来真像顺口溜
Really just roll off the tongue, don't they?

673
00:47:47,860 --> 00:47:49,660
我何时会有自己的法器？ 等你准备好的时候
When do I get my relic?

674
00:47:50,070 --> 00:47:51,120
我想我准备好了
When you're ready.

675
00:47:51,360 --> 00:47:53,960
那得由法器来决定
I think I'm ready.

676
00:47:51,455 --> 00:47:53,965
You're ready when the relic decides you're ready.

677
00:47:54,620 --> 00:47:55,870
现在…
For now...

678
00:47:56,870 --> 00:47:57,870
召唤一项武器
Conjure a weapon.

679
00:47:59,620 --> 00:48:00,620
好
All right.

680
00:48:07,050 --> 00:48:08,140
尽力反击
Fight!

681
00:48:09,300 --> 00:48:10,770
像生死交关那样拼命
Fight like your life depended on it.

682
00:48:16,970 --> 00:48:18,350
因为有一天…
Because one day...

683
00:48:18,640 --> 00:48:19,860
可能救你一命
It may.

684
00:48:39,870 --> 00:48:43,000
克莉丝汀

685
00:48:46,850 --> 00:48:51,580
克莉丝汀 我再写一封电子邮件给你

686
00:49:30,210 --> 00:49:31,210
王？
Wong?

687
00:49:43,890 --> 00:49:44,890
好
Okay.

688
00:49:45,560 --> 00:49:49,110
首先 打开阿迦莫托之眼
"First, open the eye of agamotto."

689
00:50:09,290 --> 00:50:10,510
好
All right.

690
00:50:33,820 --> 00:50:35,160
天啊
Oh, my.

691
00:50:49,842 --> 00:50:50,972
What if...

692
00:51:12,690 --> 00:51:14,070
多玛暮
"Dormammu."

693
00:51:15,820 --> 00:51:16,990
黑暗次元
"The dark dimension."

694
00:51:17,950 --> 00:51:19,410
永生？
Eternal life?

695
00:51:25,870 --> 00:51:26,870
住手
What the...

696
00:51:26,128 --> 00:51:26,998
Stop!

697
00:51:30,870 --> 00:51:33,170
破坏时间连续性是被严格禁止的
Tampering with continuum probabilities is forbidden.

698
00:51:33,420 --> 00:51:35,800
我只是照书上的指示
I was just doing exactly what it said in the book.

699
00:51:36,090 --> 00:51:37,210
书上说
What did the book say about the dangers of performing that ritual?

700
00:51:37,300 --> 00:51:38,860
执行这仪式会有什么危险？

701
00:51:38,880 --> 00:51:40,530
不知道 我还没看到那里
I don't know. I hadn't gotten to that part yet.

702
00:51:40,550 --> 00:51:43,560
操控时间可能造成时间错位
Temporal manipulations can create branches in time.

703
00:51:43,720 --> 00:51:45,970
导致次元入口失序
Unstable dimensional openings.

704
00:51:46,140 --> 00:51:48,360
空间矛盾 时间不断循环
Spatial paradoxes! Time loops!

705
00:51:48,520 --> 00:51:50,490
你想要永远重复
You wanna get stuck reliving the same moment

706
00:51:50,770 --> 00:51:51,860
同一个时刻
over and over forever...

707
00:51:51,940 --> 00:51:53,280
还是根本没存在过？
Or never having existed at all?

708
00:51:54,690 --> 00:51:56,940
他们应该在咒语前面加上警语
Really should put the warnings before the spell.

709
00:51:57,030 --> 00:51:58,990
好奇心会要人命的
Your curiosity could have gotten you killed.

710
00:51:59,280 --> 00:52:01,410
你不是在操控时空连续性
You weren't manipulating the space-time continuum...

711
00:52:01,490 --> 00:52:02,490
而是在破坏它
You were breaking it.

712
00:52:03,910 --> 00:52:05,880
我们不能窜改自然法则
We do not tamper with natural law. We defend it.

713
00:52:05,950 --> 00:52:06,950
而是要保护它

714
00:52:07,200 --> 00:52:08,500
你到底怎么弄的？
How did you even do that?

715
00:52:10,160 --> 00:52:13,040
你怎么看得懂它所需的长串咒语？
Where did you learn the litany of spells required to even understand it?

716
00:52:13,290 --> 00:52:14,350
我过目不忘
I've got a photographic memory.

717
00:52:14,380 --> 00:52:16,420
所以才能同时拿到 医师资格和博士学位
That's how I got my m.D. And ph.D. At the same time.

718
00:52:16,460 --> 00:52:17,880
你刚刚所做的…
What you just did...

719
00:52:18,630 --> 00:52:20,300
不只需要超强记忆力
Takes more than a good memory.

720
00:52:20,590 --> 00:52:22,310
你天生就是秘术高手
You were born for the mystic arts.

721
00:52:22,380 --> 00:52:24,560
但我的手还在抖
And yet my hands still shake.

722
00:52:24,800 --> 00:52:25,930
只是暂时的
For now, yes.

723
00:52:26,060 --> 00:52:27,230
不会这样一直下去吗？
Not forever?

724
00:52:27,470 --> 00:52:28,520
我们又不是算命仙
We're not prophets.

725
00:52:28,720 --> 00:52:30,600
你何时要跟我说我们的身分？
When are you gonna start telling me what we are?

726
00:52:35,810 --> 00:52:37,490
复仇者联盟那样的英雄
While heroes like the avengers

727
00:52:37,570 --> 00:52:39,860
保护世界对抗有形体的物质危险
protect the world from physical dangers...

728
00:52:39,940 --> 00:52:43,410
我们魔法师则保护世界 对抗形而上的神秘威胁
We sorcerers safeguard it against more mystical threats.

729
00:52:44,490 --> 00:52:46,960
古一是这一代的
The ancient one is the latest in a long line of sorcerers supreme...

730
00:52:47,080 --> 00:52:48,200
至尊魔法师

731
00:52:48,740 --> 00:52:52,090
他们最早可追溯到 数千年前的秘术之父
Going back thousands of years to the father of the mystic arts...

732
00:52:52,250 --> 00:52:53,370
伟大的阿迦莫托
The mighty agamotto.

733
00:52:54,420 --> 00:52:58,510
他创造了你擅自借用的这个眼睛
Same sorcerer who created the eye you so recklessly borrowed.

734
00:53:00,010 --> 00:53:03,510
阿迦莫托在能量之地 建立三座至圣所
Agamotto built three sanctums in places of power...

735
00:53:03,590 --> 00:53:05,690
那些地方如今都是大城市
Where great cities now stand.

736
00:53:05,760 --> 00:53:07,930
那道门通往香港至圣所
That door leads to the Hong Kong sanctum.

737
00:53:08,680 --> 00:53:10,560
那道门通往纽约至圣所
That door to the New York sanctum.

738
00:53:11,270 --> 00:53:12,510
那道通往伦敦至圣所
That one to the London sanctum.

739
00:53:13,440 --> 00:53:14,650
这些至圣所…
Together...

740
00:53:14,940 --> 00:53:18,360
共同在我们世界周围形成防护盾
The sanctums generate a protective shield around our world.

741
00:53:18,770 --> 00:53:20,530
至圣所保护世界
The sanctums protect the world...

742
00:53:20,610 --> 00:53:21,950
我们魔法师…
And we sorcerers...

743
00:53:22,610 --> 00:53:23,860
保护至圣所
Protect the sanctums.

744
00:53:24,110 --> 00:53:25,990
为了防范什么？
From what?

745
00:53:26,280 --> 00:53:28,780
来自其他次元的威胁
Other dimensional beings that threaten our universe.

746
00:53:29,490 --> 00:53:30,620
像是多玛暮
Like dormammu.

747
00:53:32,200 --> 00:53:33,500
你怎么知道这名字？
Where did you learn that name?

748
00:53:34,210 --> 00:53:37,380
我在《卡里欧斯卓之书》看到的 怎么了？
I just read it in the book of cagliostro. Why?

749
00:53:42,590 --> 00:53:45,140
多玛暮住在黑暗次元
Dormammu dwells in the dark dimension.

750
00:53:46,300 --> 00:53:47,300
超越时间
Beyond time.

751
00:53:48,100 --> 00:53:50,140
他是宇宙征服者
He is the cosmic conqueror...

752
00:53:50,220 --> 00:53:52,150
世界破坏者
The destroyer of worlds.

753
00:53:52,640 --> 00:53:55,990
具有无穷力量
A being of infinite power and endless hunger...

754
00:53:56,060 --> 00:53:58,480
不断想入侵每个宇宙
On a quest to invade every universe...

755
00:53:58,560 --> 00:54:01,280
将所有世界纳入他的黑暗次元
And bring all worlds into his dark dimension.

756
00:54:02,690 --> 00:54:05,160
他最渴望的就是地球
And he hungers for earth most of all.

757
00:54:06,660 --> 00:54:08,500
卡西流斯偷走的那几页
The pages that kaecilius stole.

758
00:54:08,990 --> 00:54:11,090
那仪式能联系多玛暮
A ritual to contact dormammu

759
00:54:11,160 --> 00:54:12,680
从黑暗次元汲取力量
and draw power from the dark dimension.

760
00:54:16,880 --> 00:54:18,840
好吧
Okay...

761
00:54:20,460 --> 00:54:21,510
我退出
I'm out.

762
00:54:22,170 --> 00:54:24,670
我来是为了治疗我的手
I came here to heal my hands.

763
00:54:25,420 --> 00:54:28,720
不是打什么神秘战争
Not to fight in some mystical war.

764
00:54:30,930 --> 00:54:32,020
伦敦
London.

765
00:54:36,850 --> 00:54:37,850
卡西流斯
Kaecilius!

766
00:54:38,150 --> 00:54:39,150
不！
No!

767
00:54:45,400 --> 00:54:47,250
王？莫度？
Wong? Mordo?

768
00:55:23,860 --> 00:55:25,440
177A 布里克街

769
00:55:38,210 --> 00:55:39,250
有人在吗？
Hello?

770
00:56:08,610 --> 00:56:09,610
有人在吗？
Hello?

771
00:56:48,320 --> 00:56:51,950
丹尼尔 原来是你当上这座至圣所的大师
Daniel, I see they made you master of this sanctum.

772
00:56:53,030 --> 00:56:55,160
知道那代表什么意思吗？
You know what that means?

773
00:56:55,660 --> 00:56:57,330
你将为了保护它而死
That you'll die protecting it.

774
00:57:13,340 --> 00:57:14,560
住手
Stop!

775
00:57:25,900 --> 00:57:28,240
你在卡玛泰姬待多久了…先生？
How long have you been at kamar-taj, mister...

776
00:57:28,520 --> 00:57:29,650
医生
Doctor.

777
00:57:31,110 --> 00:57:32,110
达克特先生？
Mister doctor?

778
00:57:32,650 --> 00:57:34,200
史传奇
It's strange.

779
00:57:35,820 --> 00:57:38,200
现在是流行取怪名吗？
Maybe. Who am I to judge?

780
01:00:03,350 --> 01:00:05,310
你根本不会用吧？
You don't know how to use that, do you?

781
01:01:50,450 --> 01:01:51,920
什么？
What?

782
01:01:56,960 --> 01:01:58,300
停
Stop it.

783
01:01:58,420 --> 01:01:59,420
我叫你停下来
I said stop it.

784
01:01:59,630 --> 01:02:01,070
这停不下来的 达克特先生
You cannot stop this, mister doctor.

785
01:02:01,250 --> 01:02:03,600
我根本不知道“这”是什么
I don't even know what "this" is.

786
01:02:03,760 --> 01:02:04,800
它是末日
It's the end...

787
01:02:05,130 --> 01:02:06,810
也是开始
And the beginning.

788
01:02:06,970 --> 01:02:09,720
无数次元逐渐减少 最后变成一个
The many becoming the few becoming the one.

789
01:02:11,430 --> 01:02:12,950
你要再胡言乱语
If you're not gonna start making sense...

790
01:02:12,970 --> 01:02:14,790
我就把这东西放回去
I'm just gonna have to put this thing back on.

791
01:02:14,810 --> 01:02:15,860
告诉我 达克特先生
Tell me, mister doctor...

792
01:02:16,520 --> 01:02:19,320
我是史蒂芬史传奇医生
My name is doctor Stephen strange.

793
01:02:19,610 --> 01:02:21,150
- 你是医生？ - 对
-You are a doctor? -Yeah.

794
01:02:21,320 --> 01:02:22,320
科学家
A scientist.

795
01:02:22,860 --> 01:02:24,490
你了解自然法则
You understand the laws of nature.

796
01:02:24,780 --> 01:02:27,950
万物皆会老化 皆会死去
All things age. All things die.

797
01:02:28,030 --> 01:02:29,580
我们的太阳终将烧尽
In the end, our sun burns out.

798
01:02:29,660 --> 01:02:31,910
我们的宇宙会变冷而毁灭
Our universe grows cold and perishes.

799
01:02:32,540 --> 01:02:33,790
但是黑暗次元…
But the dark dimension...

800
01:02:34,960 --> 01:02:36,630
它是个超越时间的地方
It's a place beyond time.

801
01:02:36,870 --> 01:02:38,430
够了 我把这玩意放回去
That's it. I'm putting this thing back on.

802
01:02:38,460 --> 01:02:40,020
这世界不见得要灭亡 医生
This world doesn't have to die, doctor.

803
01:02:40,130 --> 01:02:42,730
这世界能找到适当的位置 跟其他许多世界
This world can take its rightful place alongside so many others...

804
01:02:42,880 --> 01:02:44,130
构成独一宇宙
As part of the one.

805
01:02:44,840 --> 01:02:46,680
伟大而美丽的独一宇宙
The great and beautiful one.

806
01:02:47,470 --> 01:02:49,190
我们能够长生不老
We can all live forever.

807
01:02:49,510 --> 01:02:50,680
是吗？
Really?

808
01:02:52,890 --> 01:02:55,940
你从那个美丽乌托邦能得到什么？
What do you have to gain out of this new age dimensional utopia?

809
01:02:57,020 --> 01:02:58,100
跟你一样
The same as you.

810
01:02:58,270 --> 01:03:01,020
跟大家一样 生命 永生
The same as everyone. Life. Eternal life.

811
01:03:01,610 --> 01:03:03,530
人们只想到善恶
People think in terms of good and evil...

812
01:03:03,780 --> 01:03:05,540
其实时间才是我们真正的敌人
When really time is the true enemy of us all.

813
01:03:05,610 --> 01:03:07,330
时间扼杀一切
Time kills everything.

814
01:03:07,570 --> 01:03:09,160
那你杀的那些人呢？
What about the people you killed?

815
01:03:09,450 --> 01:03:10,540
微不足道
Tiny.

816
01:03:10,620 --> 01:03:13,080
冰冷宇宙中无足轻重的一粒微尘
Momentary specks within an indifferent universe.

817
01:03:15,200 --> 01:03:17,080
对 你懂
Yes. You see.

818
01:03:17,910 --> 01:03:19,920
你明白我们的所作所为
You see what we're doing.

819
01:03:20,540 --> 01:03:22,290
这世界不该如此
The world is not what it ought to be.

820
01:03:22,380 --> 01:03:24,880
人类渴望永恒
Humanity longs for the eternal...

821
01:03:24,960 --> 01:03:27,680
渴望一个超越时间的世界 因为时间奴役了我们
For a world beyond time, because time is what enslaves us.

822
01:03:27,760 --> 01:03:30,010
时间是一种羞辱
Time is an insult.

823
01:03:30,090 --> 01:03:31,720
死亡是一种羞辱
Death is an insult.

824
01:03:33,140 --> 01:03:34,390
医生
Doctor...

825
01:03:35,390 --> 01:03:37,860
我们并不希望统治世界
We don't seek to rule this world.

826
01:03:37,930 --> 01:03:39,190
我们希望拯救它
We seek to save it...

827
01:03:39,270 --> 01:03:42,770
将它交给多玛暮 他是演化的终极目标
To hand it over to dormammu, who is the intent of all evolution...

828
01:03:43,770 --> 01:03:45,620
所有生命存在的原因
The why of all existence.

829
01:03:46,610 --> 01:03:49,530
至尊魔法师才会保护生命
The sorcerer supreme defends existence.

830
01:03:50,910 --> 01:03:53,330
你为何来到卡玛泰姬 医生？
What was it that brought you to kamar-taj, doctor?

831
01:03:53,580 --> 01:03:54,830
受到启蒙吗？
Was it enlightenment?

832
01:03:55,620 --> 01:03:56,840
为了得到力量？
Power?

833
01:03:58,660 --> 01:04:01,090
你是来被治愈的 跟我们都一样
You came to be healed, as did we all.

834
01:04:02,920 --> 01:04:05,420
卡玛泰姬是个收破烂的地方
Kamar-taj is a place that collects broken things.

835
01:04:05,500 --> 01:04:07,510
我们都期望能够痊愈
We all come with the promise of being healed...

836
01:04:07,590 --> 01:04:10,430
古一却尽给我们一些魔术伎俩
And instead the ancient one gives us parlor tricks.

837
01:04:11,680 --> 01:04:14,270
真正的法术她深藏不露
The real magic she keeps for herself.

838
01:04:14,350 --> 01:04:17,690
你想过她怎么活这么久吗？
You ever wonder how she managed to live this long?

839
01:04:22,940 --> 01:04:25,280
我在卡里欧斯卓之书看到那些仪式
I saw the rituals in the book of cagliostro.

840
01:04:25,610 --> 01:04:27,780
所以你知道
So, you know.

841
01:04:28,110 --> 01:04:29,700
那仪式能给我力量
The ritual gives me the power to overthrow the ancient one...

842
01:04:29,780 --> 01:04:31,120
推翻古一

843
01:04:31,200 --> 01:04:32,950
摧毁她的至圣所
And tear her sanctums down.

844
01:04:33,030 --> 01:04:35,710
引入黑暗次元
To let the dark dimension in.

845
01:04:35,780 --> 01:04:37,790
因为古一隐藏独占的法术
Because what the ancient one hoards, dormammu gives freely.

846
01:04:38,080 --> 01:04:39,500
多玛暮却大方分享

847
01:04:40,330 --> 01:04:41,830
永生
Life everlasting.

848
01:04:42,620 --> 01:04:44,970
他不是世界的摧毁者
He's not the destroyer of worlds, doctor.

849
01:04:45,040 --> 01:04:46,970
而是救世者
He's the savior of worlds.

850
01:04:48,000 --> 01:04:49,260
不 怎么可能
No. I mean, come on.

851
01:04:49,340 --> 01:04:51,180
看看你的脸
Look at your face.

852
01:04:51,630 --> 01:04:53,730
多玛暮让你成为杀人凶手
Dormammu made you a murderer.

853
01:04:53,800 --> 01:04:56,020
他的王国能有多美好？
Just how good can his kingdom be?

854
01:04:57,970 --> 01:04:59,520
你觉得很好笑吗？
You think that's funny?

855
01:04:59,970 --> 01:05:01,650
不是
No, not that.

856
01:05:01,810 --> 01:05:04,230
好笑的是你的灵环不见了
What's funny is that you've lost your sling ring.

857
01:06:12,590 --> 01:06:13,680
先生 需要帮忙吗？
Sir, can I help you?

858
01:06:13,760 --> 01:06:14,970
帕默医师 她在哪？
Doctor Palmer, where is she?

859
01:06:15,130 --> 01:06:16,690
- 先生 我们需要… - 她在哪？
-Sir. We need to get... -Where is she?

860
01:06:16,720 --> 01:06:18,220
护理站
The nurse's station.

861
01:06:18,300 --> 01:06:19,400
克莉丝汀
Christine!

862
01:06:21,390 --> 01:06:22,620
史蒂芬？
Stephen?

863
01:06:22,640 --> 01:06:23,730
我的天啊
Oh, my god.

864
01:06:23,810 --> 01:06:26,400
马上带我进手术室 你进来就好
Get me in an operating theater now. Just you.

865
01:06:26,480 --> 01:06:27,600
快 我没时间了
Now! I haven't any time.

866
01:06:28,230 --> 01:06:29,320
发生什么事？
What happened?

867
01:06:29,400 --> 01:06:32,370
我被刺伤 心包填塞
I was stabbed. Cardiac tamponade.

868
01:06:33,400 --> 01:06:34,900
你身上穿的是什么？
What are you wearing?

869
01:06:41,580 --> 01:06:42,580
胸腔没有状况
Chest cavity is clear.

870
01:06:42,620 --> 01:06:45,370
不 心包囊出血
No, the blood is in the pericardial sac.

871
01:06:48,330 --> 01:06:49,510
不…
No, no, no.

872
01:06:49,580 --> 01:06:50,590
史蒂芬？
Stephen?

873
01:06:52,170 --> 01:06:53,390
天啊
Come on, come on.

874
01:06:55,630 --> 01:06:57,470
心跳率过低

875
01:07:19,110 --> 01:07:21,330
高一点
Just a little higher.

876
01:07:22,580 --> 01:07:23,940
用针拜托小心点
Please be careful with the needle.

877
01:07:25,870 --> 01:07:26,870
史蒂芬
Stephen?

878
01:07:29,620 --> 01:07:30,630
我看到了什么？
What am I seeing?

879
01:07:30,880 --> 01:07:32,670
我的灵体
My astral body.

880
01:07:33,960 --> 01:07:34,960
你死了吗？
Are you dead?

881
01:07:35,260 --> 01:07:36,850
不 但我快死了
No, Christine. But I am dying.

882
01:07:39,050 --> 01:07:40,930
对
Right.

883
01:07:42,390 --> 01:07:43,390
好吧
Yeah. All right.

884
01:07:44,140 --> 01:07:45,140
好
Okay.

885
01:07:48,560 --> 01:07:50,400
哇
Oh, wow.

886
01:07:54,900 --> 01:07:56,870
我没见过这种伤口
I've never seen a wound like this.

887
01:07:57,400 --> 01:07:58,820
你被什么刺伤？
What were you stabbed with?

888
01:07:59,360 --> 01:08:00,580
不知道
I don't know.

889
01:08:20,430 --> 01:08:22,100
我必须消失了
I'm gonna have to vanish now.

890
01:08:22,340 --> 01:08:23,560
什么？
What?

891
01:08:23,640 --> 01:08:25,180
让我活下去 好吗？
Keep me alive, will you?

892
01:08:28,270 --> 01:08:30,310
好
Okay.

893
01:08:54,750 --> 01:08:55,840
惨了
Oh, shit.

894
01:09:27,080 --> 01:09:28,370
充电至200焦耳

895
01:09:33,382 --> 01:09:34,552
Come on, come on.

896
01:09:39,670 --> 01:09:40,840
史蒂芬 加油
Stephen, come on.

897
01:09:43,550 --> 01:09:44,970
再来一次
Hit me again.

898
01:09:45,050 --> 01:09:46,640
不要这样吓人
Stop doing that!

899
01:09:46,930 --> 01:09:48,600
加强电流 再来一次
Up the voltage and hit me again.

900
01:09:48,680 --> 01:09:49,730
不 你的心脏在跳了
No, your heart's beating!

901
01:09:49,890 --> 01:09:51,140
动手就是了
Just do it!

902
01:09:52,770 --> 01:09:53,770
天啊
Oh, my god.

903
01:09:55,000 --> 01:09:55,600
选择电流强度：（焦耳）

904
01:09:59,210 --> 01:10:00,320
充电至360焦耳

905
01:10:00,320 --> 01:10:00,900
请勿碰触病患 按下电击按钮

906
01:10:22,710 --> 01:10:24,720
天啊…
Oh, god! Oh, god!

907
01:10:24,880 --> 01:10:25,970
你还好吗？
Are you okay?

908
01:10:26,050 --> 01:10:27,140
嗯
Yeah.

909
01:10:27,220 --> 01:10:28,340
好
Okay.

910
01:10:34,770 --> 01:10:36,820
过了这么久
After all this time...

911
01:10:36,980 --> 01:10:38,780
你突然出现在这里
You just show up here...

912
01:10:40,310 --> 01:10:42,410
飞出自己的身体
Flying out of your body.

913
01:10:42,570 --> 01:10:44,290
我知道
Yeah, I know.

914
01:10:44,440 --> 01:10:45,990
对了 我也很想你
I missed you, too, by the way.

915
01:10:46,860 --> 01:10:47,960
哈哈
Ha ha.

916
01:10:48,030 --> 01:10:50,660
我写电邮给你 你都没回
I wrote you emails, but you never responded.

917
01:10:50,740 --> 01:10:51,990
我干嘛回？
Why would I?

918
01:10:52,910 --> 01:10:55,210
克莉丝汀 我真的非常抱歉
Christine, I am so, so sorry.

919
01:10:56,290 --> 01:10:58,130
你说的都对
For all of it. You were right.

920
01:10:58,330 --> 01:11:01,930
我是个大猪头 对你真的很坏
I was a complete asshole. I treated you so horribly.

921
01:11:02,000 --> 01:11:04,430
你值得被好好珍惜
And you deserved so much more.

922
01:11:04,670 --> 01:11:06,050
住口 你惊吓过度了
Stop. You're clearly in shock.

923
01:11:07,970 --> 01:11:10,310
到底发生什么事？
What the hell is happening?

924
01:11:10,470 --> 01:11:11,770
你到哪去了？
Where have you been?

925
01:11:13,680 --> 01:11:15,770
西医对我束手无策
After western medicine failed me...

926
01:11:15,930 --> 01:11:18,900
我往东方去 最后到了加德满都
I headed east, and I ended up in kathmandu.

927
01:11:19,190 --> 01:11:20,190
加德满都？
Kathmandu?

928
01:11:20,230 --> 01:11:21,530
对
Yeah.

929
01:11:22,400 --> 01:11:23,700
像巴布席格那首歌？
Like the Bob seger song?

930
01:11:24,030 --> 01:11:25,780
1975年 《美丽失败者》 A面
1975, beautiful loser, side a. Yeah.

931
01:11:26,030 --> 01:11:29,660
我到了一个叫卡玛泰姬的地方
I went to a place called kamar-taj...

932
01:11:29,820 --> 01:11:33,500
跟一个叫古一的人交谈
And I talked to someone called "the ancient one."

933
01:11:34,200 --> 01:11:35,620
所以你加入邪教
So you joined a cult.

934
01:11:35,700 --> 01:11:38,300
没有 不算是
No, I didn't. No, not exactly. No.

935
01:11:38,500 --> 01:11:41,220
他们教我开发我不知道的力量
They did teach me to tap into powers that I never even knew existed.

936
01:11:41,330 --> 01:11:42,630
听起来就像邪教
Yeah. That sounds like a cult.

937
01:11:42,880 --> 01:11:44,050
那不是邪教
It's not a cult.

938
01:11:44,300 --> 01:11:45,770
邪教信徒都这么说
That's what a cultist would say.

939
01:11:45,800 --> 01:11:46,800
不
Oh, no.

940
01:11:47,380 --> 01:11:49,850
等等 史蒂芬 你想干嘛？
Wait. Stephen, wait. What do you think you're doing?

941
01:11:50,090 --> 01:11:51,720
邪教聚会快迟到了
I'm late for a cult meeting.

942
01:11:55,520 --> 01:11:56,610
这实在太扯了
This is insane.

943
01:11:56,680 --> 01:11:57,770
是啊
Yeah.

944
01:11:57,850 --> 01:11:59,850
你要去哪？
Where are you going?

945
01:12:00,390 --> 01:12:01,820
你能跟我说实话吗？
Can you tell me the truth?

946
01:12:02,730 --> 01:12:06,200
有个信奉某种古老形体的强大法师
A powerful sorcerer who gave himself over to an ancient entity...

947
01:12:06,360 --> 01:12:08,990
他能改变物理法则 千方百计要杀我
Can bend the very laws of physics, tried very hard to kill me.

948
01:12:09,070 --> 01:12:10,920
但我把他拴在格林威治村
But I left him chained up in greenwich village...

949
01:12:10,950 --> 01:12:13,510
回到那里最快的办法 就是穿过我在清洁工具间
And the quickest way back there is through a dimensional gateway...

950
01:12:13,530 --> 01:12:14,680
打开的异次元入口
That I opened up in the mop closet.

951
01:12:14,700 --> 01:12:16,580
好吧 别告诉我
Okay. Don't tell me. Fine.

952
01:12:27,130 --> 01:12:28,720
我真的该走了
Really do have to go.

953
01:12:29,800 --> 01:12:30,890
喔
Yeah.

954
01:13:16,760 --> 01:13:17,760
史传奇
Strange!

955
01:13:20,270 --> 01:13:21,520
你没事
You're okay.

956
01:13:21,770 --> 01:13:23,860
相较之下 我算没事
A relative term. But yeah, I'm okay.

957
01:13:24,650 --> 01:13:26,400
魔浮斗篷
The cloak of levitation.

958
01:13:27,440 --> 01:13:28,910
它找上了你
It came to you.

959
01:13:29,690 --> 01:13:31,110
这可不容易
No minor feat.

960
01:13:32,070 --> 01:13:33,490
它喜怒无常
It's a fickle thing.

961
01:13:33,700 --> 01:13:35,660
他逃走了 卡西流斯？
He's escaped.

962
01:13:35,950 --> 01:13:36,950
对
Kaecilius?

963
01:13:37,530 --> 01:13:39,750
他能任意摺叠空间和物体
Yeah.

964
01:13:37,876 --> 01:13:40,166
He can fold space and matter at will.

965
01:13:39,990 --> 01:13:43,370
他能摺叠镜次元之外的物体
He folds matter outside the mirror dimension...

966
01:13:43,540 --> 01:13:44,630
在现实世界里？
In the real world?

967
01:13:44,830 --> 01:13:45,830
是
Yeah.

968
01:13:46,000 --> 01:13:47,800
还有几个？ 两个
How many more?

969
01:13:48,670 --> 01:13:50,890
我把其中一个困在沙漠里
Two.

970
01:13:49,012 --> 01:13:51,142
I stranded one in the desert.

971
01:13:50,960 --> 01:13:52,060
另一个呢？
And the other?

972
01:13:52,130 --> 01:13:53,600
他的身体在走廊
His body's in the hall.

973
01:13:53,670 --> 01:13:55,470
杜朗大师在门厅
Master drumm is in the foyer.

974
01:13:55,720 --> 01:13:57,350
他被带回卡玛泰姬了
He's been taken back to kamar-taj.

975
01:13:57,430 --> 01:13:59,070
伦敦至圣所沦陷了
The London sanctum has fallen.

976
01:13:59,100 --> 01:14:01,350
现在只剩纽约和香港
Only New York and Hong Kong remain now...

977
01:14:01,600 --> 01:14:03,600
保护我们不沦落到黑暗次元
To shield us from the dark dimension.

978
01:14:04,390 --> 01:14:07,240
你让纽约至圣所躲过攻击
You defended the New York sanctum from attack.

979
01:14:07,480 --> 01:14:09,230
如今它的大师出缺 需要再找一个
With its master gone, it needs another.

980
01:14:09,480 --> 01:14:10,900
史传奇大师
Master strange.

981
01:14:13,780 --> 01:14:14,780
不
No.

982
01:14:15,990 --> 01:14:17,990
我是史传奇医师
It is doctor strange.

983
01:14:18,070 --> 01:14:20,790
不是史传奇大师 不是史传奇先生
Not master strange. Not mister strange.

984
01:14:20,870 --> 01:14:22,040
史传奇医师
Doctor strange.

985
01:14:23,450 --> 01:14:26,920
我当上医生时曾发誓不伤害人
When I became a doctor, i swore an oath to do no harm.

986
01:14:27,000 --> 01:14:28,340
我却杀了一个人
And I have just killed a man!

987
01:14:28,420 --> 01:14:30,260
下不为例
I'm not doing that again.

988
01:14:30,340 --> 01:14:32,810
我当医生是为了救人 不是杀人
I became a doctor to save lives, not take them.

989
01:14:33,050 --> 01:14:36,220
你当医生只为了救一个人
You became a doctor to save one life above all others.

990
01:14:36,300 --> 01:14:37,300
你自己
Your own.

991
01:14:38,890 --> 01:14:40,560
你还是看穿我了 是吧？
Still seeing through me, are you?

992
01:14:40,760 --> 01:14:44,390
我看到的东西没变 你过度膨胀的自我
I see what I've always seen: Your over-inflated ego.

993
01:14:44,930 --> 01:14:48,110
你想回到那个以为 你能掌控一切的幻象
You want to go back to the delusion that you can control anything...

994
01:14:48,270 --> 01:14:49,610
甚至死亡
Even death...

995
01:14:49,810 --> 01:14:51,410
但谁都无法掌控死亡
Which no one can control.

996
01:14:51,570 --> 01:14:54,240
连伟大的史传奇医师都没办法
Not even the great doctor Stephen strange.

997
01:14:54,490 --> 01:14:56,580
连多玛暮也不能吗？
Not even dormammu?

998
01:14:58,240 --> 01:15:00,080
他说我们能永生不死
He offers immortality.

999
01:15:00,240 --> 01:15:02,240
多玛暮的生命来自我们怕死
It's our fear of death that gives dormammu life.

1000
01:15:02,540 --> 01:15:03,630
他靠那种能量而壮大
He feeds off it.

1001
01:15:03,700 --> 01:15:06,050
就像你靠他才壮大？
Like you feed off him?

1002
01:15:06,120 --> 01:15:07,970
你跟我谈掌控死亡？
You talk to me about controlling death?

1003
01:15:08,040 --> 01:15:09,130
我知道你的秘诀
I know how you do it.

1004
01:15:09,210 --> 01:15:12,010
我看过卡里欧斯卓之书上 遗失的仪式内容
I've seen the missing rituals from the book of cagliostro.

1005
01:15:13,050 --> 01:15:15,920
接下来说话当心点 医生
Measure your next words very carefully, doctor.

1006
01:15:16,170 --> 01:15:17,890
因为你不爽听？
Because you might not like them?

1007
01:15:18,220 --> 01:15:21,020
因为你根本不懂自己说出口的话
Because you may not know of what you speak.

1008
01:15:21,260 --> 01:15:22,760
他在说什么？
What is he talking about?

1009
01:15:22,930 --> 01:15:26,230
我在说她这么长寿 永生不老的原因
I'm talking about her long life, the source of her immortality.

1010
01:15:27,810 --> 01:15:31,270
她靠汲取黑暗次元的力量存活
She draws power from the dark dimension to stay alive.

1011
01:15:33,230 --> 01:15:34,360
并不是
That's not true.

1012
01:15:34,610 --> 01:15:36,740
我解析了那些仪式
I've seen the rituals. Worked them out.

1013
01:15:37,650 --> 01:15:39,030
我知道你如何办到
I know how you do it.

1014
01:15:40,740 --> 01:15:42,160
他们一旦重新整合
Once they regroup...

1015
01:15:42,410 --> 01:15:43,910
狂热者就会回来
The zealots will be back.

1016
01:15:44,620 --> 01:15:46,460
你需要外力协助
You'll need reinforcements.

1017
01:15:53,880 --> 01:15:55,430
她不是你所想的那样
She's not who you think she is.

1018
01:15:55,630 --> 01:15:57,470
你没有立场这么说
You don't have the right to say that.

1019
01:15:57,720 --> 01:16:00,310
你不知道她肩负着多大责任
You've no idea the responsibility that rests upon her shoulders.

1020
01:16:00,380 --> 01:16:02,310
对 我也不想知道
No, and I don't want to know.

1021
01:16:02,720 --> 01:16:03,770
你这懦夫
You're a coward.

1022
01:16:04,140 --> 01:16:05,190
因为我不是杀人凶手？
Because I'm not a killer?

1023
01:16:05,430 --> 01:16:06,950
这些狂热者会杀光我们
These zealots will snuff us all out...

1024
01:16:07,020 --> 01:16:09,610
你不能集中力量先歼灭他们吗？
And you can't muster the strength to snuff them first?

1025
01:16:09,810 --> 01:16:11,290
你以为我刚刚做了什么？
What do you think I just did?

1026
01:16:11,310 --> 01:16:12,530
你救了自己一命
You saved your own life!

1027
01:16:13,900 --> 01:16:16,450
然后又抱怨个不停
And then whined about it like a wounded dog.

1028
01:16:16,650 --> 01:16:18,130
难道你杀人像喝水一样简单？
You would have done it so easily?

1029
01:16:18,150 --> 01:16:20,830
你不知道我做过什么
You've no idea the things I've done.

1030
01:16:22,990 --> 01:16:24,870
没有错
And the answer is yes.

1031
01:16:24,950 --> 01:16:26,670
我杀人不眨眼
Without hesitation.

1032
01:16:26,910 --> 01:16:28,030
即使还有其他办法？
Even if there's another way?

1033
01:16:28,200 --> 01:16:30,000
没有其他办法
There is no other way.

1034
01:16:30,160 --> 01:16:31,460
你缺乏想像力
You lack imagination.

1035
01:16:31,540 --> 01:16:32,630
不 史蒂芬
No, Stephen.

1036
01:16:32,920 --> 01:16:36,340
是你没种
You lack a spine.

1037
01:16:41,470 --> 01:16:42,680
他们回来了
They're back.

1038
01:16:49,430 --> 01:16:50,780
我们得把他们解决掉
We have to end this.

1039
01:16:50,980 --> 01:16:52,070
动手
Now!

1040
01:16:57,360 --> 01:16:58,410
史传奇
Strange!

1041
01:16:58,650 --> 01:17:00,240
下来对抗他们
Get down here and fight!

1042
01:17:00,570 --> 01:17:01,660
不！
No!

1043
01:17:06,080 --> 01:17:07,370
镜次元
The mirror dimension.

1044
01:17:07,990 --> 01:17:10,370
你在这里无法影响现实世界
You can't affect the real world in here.

1045
01:17:10,870 --> 01:17:12,170
现在该笑的是谁？
Who's laughing now?

1046
01:17:12,370 --> 01:17:13,500
混蛋
Asshole.

1047
01:17:15,380 --> 01:17:16,420
是我
I am.

1048
01:17:30,720 --> 01:17:31,740
我拿到他的灵环了
I've got his sling ring. They can't escape, right?

1049
01:17:31,770 --> 01:17:32,770
他们逃不掉了吧？

1050
01:17:34,190 --> 01:17:35,280
快跑！
Run!

1051
01:17:52,500 --> 01:17:54,140
他们与黑暗次元的关联
Their connection to the dark dimension

1052
01:17:54,170 --> 01:17:56,090
使他们在镜次元中更强大
makes them more powerful in the mirror dimension.

1053
01:17:56,170 --> 01:17:58,560
他们无法影响现实世界 却还是能杀死我们
They can't affect the real world, but they can still kill us.

1054
01:17:58,590 --> 01:18:01,430
这样并不明智 反而是自杀
This wasn't cleverness. It was suicide!

1055
01:18:16,360 --> 01:18:20,200
众妙之门

1056
01:18:18,020 --> 01:18:20,240
太爆笑了
That is hilarious.

1057
01:19:06,650 --> 01:19:08,200
这完全是个错误
This was a mistake.

1058
01:20:40,660 --> 01:20:41,790
果然没错
It's true.

1059
01:20:42,710 --> 01:20:46,090
她确实从黑暗次元汲取法力
She does draw power from the dark dimension.

1060
01:20:49,590 --> 01:20:50,640
卡西流斯
Kaecilius.

1061
01:20:53,550 --> 01:20:56,270
我来找你时身心俱疲
I came to you broken...

1062
01:20:56,600 --> 01:20:59,270
彷徨无助
Lost, in need.

1063
01:20:59,520 --> 01:21:02,270
我把你当成导师 你却满口谎言
Trusted you to be my teacher, and you fed me lies.

1064
01:21:02,770 --> 01:21:04,240
我是想保护你
I tried to protect you.

1065
01:21:04,480 --> 01:21:06,730
不让我知道真相吗？ 不让你伤害自己
From the truth?

1066
01:21:06,980 --> 01:21:09,110
现在我有了新导师
From yourself.

1067
01:21:07,159 --> 01:21:09,449
I have a new teacher now.

1068
01:21:09,440 --> 01:21:10,620
多玛暮骗你
Dormammu deceives you.

1069
01:21:11,610 --> 01:21:13,910
你不知道他的真面目
You have no idea what he truly is.

1070
01:21:14,110 --> 01:21:17,960
他的永生不是天堂 而是苦难
His eternal life is not paradise, but torment.

1071
01:21:18,120 --> 01:21:19,340
骗人
Liar.

1072
01:22:15,090 --> 01:22:16,180
克莉丝汀
Christine!

1073
01:22:17,180 --> 01:22:18,600
开什么玩笑？
Are you kidding me?

1074
01:22:19,760 --> 01:22:20,760
天啊
Oh, my god.

1075
01:22:23,310 --> 01:22:25,530
不是心房颤动 她心肌顿抑
It's not fibrillation. She has a stunned myocardium.

1076
01:22:25,600 --> 01:22:26,800
- 神经引起的？ - 对
-Neurogenic? -Yes.

1077
01:22:31,820 --> 01:22:33,030
谁去拿棉花棒
Someone get the swabs.

1078
01:22:35,530 --> 01:22:36,530
尼克
Nic?

1079
01:22:39,870 --> 01:22:41,630
我们得降低她的脑压
We need to relieve the pressure on her brain.

1080
01:22:44,200 --> 01:22:46,380
她心跳率继续下降
She's still dropping.

1081
01:22:46,460 --> 01:22:47,500
她快不行了
-We're losing her! -We need to increase her oxygen!

1082
01:22:47,580 --> 01:22:48,840
增加她的氧气

1083
01:22:49,040 --> 01:22:50,040
我需要急救车
-I need a crash cart! -Her pupils have dilated!

1084
01:22:50,090 --> 01:22:51,410
她瞳孔放大

1085
01:22:51,880 --> 01:22:52,880
没反射反应
No reflexes. We're not reading any brain activity.

1086
01:22:52,960 --> 01:22:54,440
看不到脑部活动

1087
01:23:06,060 --> 01:23:07,530
你在干嘛？
What are you doing?

1088
01:23:08,480 --> 01:23:10,230
别这样 你快死了
Come on, you're dying!

1089
01:23:18,860 --> 01:23:21,410
你得立刻回到你的肉体 没时间了
You have to return to your body now. You don't have time.

1090
01:23:21,530 --> 01:23:23,210
时间是相对的
Time is relative.

1091
01:23:23,290 --> 01:23:25,580
你还不懂
Your body hasn't even hit the floor yet.

1092
01:23:27,500 --> 01:23:29,300
我花了这么多年
I've spent so many years...

1093
01:23:29,370 --> 01:23:31,090
窥探未来
Peering through time...

1094
01:23:31,250 --> 01:23:33,750
看着眼前这一刻
Looking at this exact moment.

1095
01:23:33,840 --> 01:23:35,460
但却看不透它
But I can't see past it.

1096
01:23:36,130 --> 01:23:39,680
我避开了无数可怕的未来
I've prevented countless, terrible futures.

1097
01:23:39,760 --> 01:23:42,350
每个未来之后总是有另一个
And after each one, there's always another.

1098
01:23:42,430 --> 01:23:44,810
它们全都导向这里
And they all lead here...

1099
01:23:44,890 --> 01:23:45,890
却不再往前
But never further.

1100
01:23:46,140 --> 01:23:48,110
你认为你的死期到了
You think this is where you die.

1101
01:23:49,020 --> 01:23:51,400
想知道我在你的未来看到什么吗？
You wonder what I see in your future?

1102
01:23:51,480 --> 01:23:52,610
不想
No.

1103
01:23:54,530 --> 01:23:55,990
想
Yes.

1104
01:23:56,070 --> 01:23:57,620
我始终没看到你的未来
I never saw your future.

1105
01:23:57,900 --> 01:24:00,250
只看到它的可能性
Only its possibilities.

1106
01:24:00,320 --> 01:24:03,040
你具有强大的行善能力
You have such a capacity for goodness.

1107
01:24:03,240 --> 01:24:05,120
你一向出类拔萃
You always excelled...

1108
01:24:05,200 --> 01:24:07,710
但不是因为你渴望成功
But not because you craved success...

1109
01:24:07,790 --> 01:24:10,260
而是你害怕失败
But because of your fear of failure.

1110
01:24:10,330 --> 01:24:12,080
所以我才成为一个杰出的医生
That's what made me a great doctor.

1111
01:24:12,290 --> 01:24:14,890
那正是阻止你更伟大的障碍
It's precisely what kept you from greatness.

1112
01:24:16,000 --> 01:24:18,050
傲慢与恐惧
Arrogance and fear still keep you...

1113
01:24:18,130 --> 01:24:19,510
依然让你无法学会
From learning the simplest and most significant lesson of all.

1114
01:24:19,590 --> 01:24:21,640
最简单最重要的教训

1115
01:24:21,720 --> 01:24:22,720
那是？
Which is?

1116
01:24:24,970 --> 01:24:27,190
重点不在你身上
It's not about you.

1117
01:24:30,980 --> 01:24:32,280
当你第一次来找我
When you first came to me...

1118
01:24:32,350 --> 01:24:35,530
你问我如何治愈强纳森潘柏恩
You asked me how I was able to heal Jonathan pangborn.

1119
01:24:36,530 --> 01:24:37,820
我没有
I didn't.

1120
01:24:39,740 --> 01:24:43,990
他将次元能量直接注入自己身体
He channels dimensional energy directly into his own body.

1121
01:24:44,160 --> 01:24:45,910
他利用法力让自己走路？
He uses magic to walk?

1122
01:24:45,990 --> 01:24:47,170
一直如此
Constantly.

1123
01:24:47,740 --> 01:24:49,590
他有选择
He had a choice...

1124
01:24:50,370 --> 01:24:52,340
重返自己的生活
To return to his own life...

1125
01:24:52,920 --> 01:24:55,210
或是追求比自己更大的目标
Or to serve something greater than himself.

1126
01:24:55,290 --> 01:24:57,970
所以我的手可以恢复正常？
So I could have my hands back again?

1127
01:24:58,050 --> 01:24:59,470
重拾过去的生活？
My old life?

1128
01:25:00,130 --> 01:25:01,380
可以
You could.

1129
01:25:02,470 --> 01:25:05,270
那么世界只会变得更悲惨
And the world would be all the lesser for it.

1130
01:25:06,850 --> 01:25:10,150
我厌恶从黑暗次元汲取能量
I've hated drawing power from the dark dimension.

1131
01:25:10,230 --> 01:25:11,400
但你很清楚
But as you well know...

1132
01:25:11,480 --> 01:25:13,850
有时必须打破陈规
Sometimes one must break the rules...

1133
01:25:13,940 --> 01:25:15,740
才能成就更远大的目标
In order to serve the greater good.

1134
01:25:15,980 --> 01:25:17,900
莫度可不会这么想
Mordo won't see it that way.

1135
01:25:17,980 --> 01:25:20,610
莫度的灵魂严谨而僵化
Mordo's soul is rigid and unmovable...

1136
01:25:20,690 --> 01:25:22,910
因为年轻时经历太多风雨
Forged by the fires of his youth.

1137
01:25:23,160 --> 01:25:24,910
他需要你的弹性
He needs your flexibility...

1138
01:25:24,990 --> 01:25:27,040
一如你需要他的定力
Just as you need his strength.

1139
01:25:28,160 --> 01:25:31,840
你们联手才有可能阻止多玛暮
Only together do you stand a chance of stopping dormammu.

1140
01:25:32,080 --> 01:25:33,550
我还没准备好
I'm not ready.

1141
01:25:35,630 --> 01:25:37,050
从来没有人准备好
No one ever is.

1142
01:25:38,710 --> 01:25:40,890
我们无法选择时机
We don't get to choose our time.

1143
01:25:45,010 --> 01:25:47,230
死亡赋予生命意义
Death is what gives life meaning.

1144
01:25:48,350 --> 01:25:50,940
让人知道日子有限
To know your days are numbered.

1145
01:25:51,020 --> 01:25:53,060
人生苦短
Your time is short.

1146
01:25:55,020 --> 01:25:57,320
你以为过了这么久 我应该准备好了
You'd think after all this time, I'd be ready.

1147
01:25:58,270 --> 01:25:59,990
但看看我
But look at me.

1148
01:26:00,070 --> 01:26:03,070
将一个时刻不断延长
Stretching one moment out into a thousand...

1149
01:26:03,320 --> 01:26:05,660
就为了赏雪
Just so that I can watch the snow.

1150
01:26:44,400 --> 01:26:45,830
你还好吗？
Are you okay?

1151
01:26:53,620 --> 01:26:55,750
我不懂到底是怎么一回事
I don't understand what's happening.

1152
01:26:55,910 --> 01:26:57,010
我知道
I know.

1153
01:26:57,790 --> 01:27:00,670
但我现在必须离开
But I have to go away now.

1154
01:27:05,590 --> 01:27:08,470
你说失去双手不是世界末日
You said that losing my hands didn't have to be the end.

1155
01:27:08,550 --> 01:27:10,230
反而可能是开始
That it could be a beginning.

1156
01:27:10,430 --> 01:27:11,480
是啊
Yeah.

1157
01:27:12,970 --> 01:27:15,690
因为还有其他方式可以救人
Because there are other ways to save lives.

1158
01:27:18,810 --> 01:27:20,310
更困难的方式
A harder way.

1159
01:27:22,570 --> 01:27:24,820
更奇怪的方式
A weirder way.

1160
